quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  40,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  40,1,h m
  40,2,"iss kitaab ka nuzool Allah ki taraf se hai jo zabardast hai, sab kuch jan-nay wala hai"
  40,3,"gunah maaf karne wala aur tauba qubool karne wala hai, sakht saza dainay wala aur bara sahib fazl hai koi mabood is ke siwa nahi, usi ki taraf sab ko palatna hai"
  40,4,Allah ki ayaat mein jhagrre nahi karte magar sirf woh log jinhon ne kufar kya hai iss ke baad duniya ke mulkon mein unn kichallat phirat tumhe kisi dhokay mein nah daaley
  40,5,"inn se pehlay Nooh ki qoum bhi jhutla chuki hai, aur uss ke baad bohat se dosray jathon ne bhi yeh kaam kya hai har qoum apne rasool par jhpti taakay ussay girftar kere unn sab ne baatil ke hathyaaron se haq ko neecha dikhaane ki koshish ki magar aakhir-kaar mein ne un ko pakar liya, phir dekh lau ke meri saza kaisi sakht thi"
  40,6,isi terhan tairay rab ka yeh faisla bhi unn sab logon par chaspan ho chuka hai jo kufar ke murtakib hue hain ke woh wasil jahannum honay walay hain
  40,7,"arsh Ellahi ke haamil farishtay aur woh jo arsh ke gird o paish haazir rehtay hain, sab apne rab ki hamd ke sath is ki tasbeeh kar rahay hain woh is par imaan rakhtay hain aur imaan laane walon ke haq mein duaye mughfirat karte hain woh kehte hain :"" ae hamaray rab, to apni rehmat aur apne ilm ke sath har cheez par chaaya howa hai, pas maaf kar day aur azaab dozakh se bacha le unn logon ko jinhon ne tauba ki hai aur tera rasta ikhtiyar kar liya hai"
  40,8,"ae hamaray rab, aur daakhil kar unn ko hamesha rehne wali unnjannaton mein jin ka to ne unn se wada kya hai, aur unn ke walidain aur biwion aur aulaad mein se jo Saleh hon ( unn ko bhi wahan unn ke sath pouncha day ) to bulaa shuba Qadir mutlaq aur hakeem hai"
  40,9,"aur bacha day unn ko buraiyon se jis ko to ne qayamat ke din buraiyon se bacha diya uss par to ne bara reham kya, yahi barri kamyabi hai """
  40,10,"jin logon ne kufar kya hai, qayamat ke roz unn ko pukaar kar kaha jaye ga"" aaj tumhe jitna shadeed gussa apne oopar aa raha hai, Allah tum par uss se ziyada ghazab naak uss waqt hota tha jab tumhe imaan ki taraf bulaya jata tha aur tum kufar karte thay """
  40,11,"woh kahin ge"" ae hamaray rab, to ne waqai hamein do dafaa mout aur do dafaa zindagi day di, ab hum apneKasoroo-n ka aitraaf karte hain, kya ab yahan se niklny ki bhi koi Sabeel hai? """
  40,12,"( jawab miley ga )"" yeh haalat jis mein tum mubtala ho, iss wajah se hai ke jab akailey Allah ki taraf bulaya jata tha to tum maan-ne se inkaar kar dete thay aur jab uss ke sath dosaron ko milaya jata to tum maan letay thay ab faisla Allah buzurag o bartar ke haath hai """
  40,13,"wohi hai jo tum ko apni nishanain dekhata hai aur aasman se tumahray liye rizaq nazil karta hai, magar ( inn nshanyon ke mushahiday se ) sabaq sirf wohi shakhs laita hai jo Allah ki taraf rujoo karne wala ho"
  40,14,"( pas ae rujoo karne walo ) Allah hi ko poukaro apne deen ko uss ke liye khalis kar ke, khuwa tumhara yeh feal kafiroon ko kitna hi nagawaar ho"
  40,15,"woh buland darjon wala, maalik arsh hai apne bundon mein se jis par chahta hai apne hukum se rooh nazil kar deta hai taakay woh mulaqaat ke din se khabardaar kar day"
  40,16,"woh din jabkay sab log be parda hon ge, Allah se un ki koi baat bhi chhupi hui nah ho gi ( uss roz pukaar kar poocha jaye ga ) aaj badshahi kis ki hai? ( sara aalam pukaar utthay ga ) Allah wahid Qahar ki"
  40,17,( kaha jaye ga ) aaj har mutnaqas ko uss kamaai ka badla diya jaye ga jo is ne ki thi aaj kisi par koi zulm nah ho ga aur Allah hisaab lainay mein bohat taiz hai
  40,18,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, dara do inn logon ko uss din se jo qareeb aa laga hai jab kaleje mun ko aa rahay hon ge aur log chup chaap gham ke ghoont piyay kharray hunge zaalmon ka nah koi Mushfiq dost ho ga aur nah koi Shafi jis ki baat maani jaye"
  40,19,Allah nigahon ki chori taq se waaqif hai aur woh raaz taq jaanta hai jo seenon ne chhupa rakhay hain
  40,20,"aur Allah theek theek be laag faisla karega rahay woh jin ko ( yeh mushriqeen ) Allah ko chore kar pkarte hain, woh kisi cheez ka bhi faisla karne walay nahi hain bilashuba Allah hi sab kuch suneney aur dekhnay wala hai"
  40,21,kya yeh log kabhi zameen mein chalay phiray nahi hain ke inhen unn logon ka injaam nazar aata jo inn se pehlay guzar chuke hain? woh inn ziyada taaqat war thay aur un se ziyada zabardast assaar zameen mein chore gay hain magar Allah ne un ke gunaaho par inhen pakar liya aur unn ko Allah se bachanay wala koi nah tha
  40,22,"yeh un ka injaam is liye howa ke un ke paas unn ke rasoolbayyanaat le kar aeye aur unhon ne maan-ne se inkaar kar diya aakhir-kaar Allah ne un ko pakar liya, yaqeenan woh barri qowat wala aur saza dainay mein bohat sakht hai"
  40,23,hum ne moose ko
  40,24,"firaon aur Haman aur qaroon ki taraf apne nshanyon aur numaya sanad mamoriyat ke sath bheja, magar unhon ne kaha"" sahir hai, kazzab hai """
  40,25,"phir jab woh hamari taraf se haq un ke samnay le aaya to unhon ne kaha"" jo log imaan laa kar is ke sath shaamil hue hain un sab ke larkoon ko qatal karo aur larkiyan ko jeeta chore do"" magar kafiroon ki chaal akart hi gayi"
  40,26,"aik roz firaon ne apne drbaryon se kaha"" chhorro mujhe, mein iss moose ko qatal kiye deta hon, aur pukaar dekhe yeh apne rab ko mujhe andesha hai ke yeh tumhara deen badal daaley ga, ya malik mein fasaad barpaa kere ga """
  40,27,"moose ne kaha"" mein ne to har uss mutaqabbir ke muqablay mein jo Yom ul hisaab par imaan nahi rakhta apne ray bay aur tumahray rab ki panah le li hai """
  40,28,"is mauqa par all firaon mein se aik momin shakhs, jo apna imaan chupaye hue tha, bol utha :"" kya tumshakhs ko sirf iss bana par qatal kar do ge ke woh kehta hai mera rab Allah hai? halaank woh tumahray rab ki taraf se tumahray paas bayyaynaat le aaya agar woh jhoota hai to is ka jhoot khud isi par palat parre ga lekin agar woh sacha hai to jin holnaak nataij ka woh tum ko khauf dilaata hai un mein se kuch to tum par zaroor hi aa jayen ge Allah kisi shakhs ko hadaayat nahi deta jo hadd se guzar jaane wala aur kazzab ho"
  40,29,"ae meri qoum ke logo! aaj tumhe badshahi haasil hai aur zameen mein tum ghalib ho, lekin agar khuda ka azaab hum par aa gaya to phir kon hai jo hamari madad kar sakay ga"" firaon ne kaha"" mein to tum logon ko wohi raye day raha hon jo mujhe munasib nazar aati hai aur mein usi rastay ki taraf tumhari rahnumai karta hon jo theek hai """
  40,30,"woh shakhs jo imaan laya tha uss ne kaha"" ae meri qoum ke logo, mujhe khauf hai ke kahin tum par bhi woh din nah aa jaye jo is se pehlay bohat se jathon par aa chuka hai"
  40,31,jaissa din qoum Nooh aur Aad aur smod aur un ke baad wali qomon par aaya tha aur yeh haqeeqat hai ke Allah apne bundon par zulm ka koi iradah nahi rakhta
  40,32,"ae qoum, mujhe dar hai ke kahin tum par faryaad o fugaah ka din nah aa jaye"
  40,33,"jab tum aik dosray ko poukaro ge aur bhage bhage phiro ge, magar uss waqt Allah se bachanay wala koi nah ho ga sach yeh hai ke jisay Allah bhatka day ussay phir koi rasta dikhaane wala nahi hota"
  40,34,"is se pehlay yousuf tumahray paas bayyaynaat le kar aeye thay magar tum unn ki layi hui taleem ki taraf se shak hi mein parre rahay phir jab unn ka intqaal ho gaya to tum ne kaha ab unn ke baad Allah koi rasool hargiz nah beje ga"" isi terhan Allah unn sab logon ko gumraahi mein daal deta hai jo hadd se guzarnay walay aur shakki hotay hain"
  40,35,aur Allah ki ayaat mein jhagrre karte hain baghair is ke ke un ke paas koi sanad ya Daleel aayi ho yeh rawayya Allah aur imaan laane walon ke nazdeek sakht mabghoz (bezari ki baat) hai isi terhan Allah har munkiro Jabbar ke dil par thpah laga deta hai
  40,36,"firaon ne kaha"" ae Haman , mere liye aik buland imarat bana taakay mein raastoon taq poanch sakun"
  40,37,"asmano ke raastoon taq, aur moose ke khuda ko jhaank kar daikhon mujhe to yeh moose jhoota hi maloom hota hai"" is terhan firaon ke liye is ki bad amli khushnuma bana di gayi aur woh raah raast se rok diya gaya firaon ki saari chaal baazi ( uss ki apni ) tabahi ke rasta hi mein sirf hui"
  40,38,"woh shakhs jo imaan laya tha, bola"" ae meri qoum ke logo, meri baat manu, mein tumhe sahih rasta batata hon"
  40,39,"ae qoum, yeh duniya ki zindagi to chand roza hai, hamesha ke qiyam ki jagah akhirat hi hai"
  40,40,"jo buraiee kere ga uss ko itna hi badla miley ga jitni uss ne buraiee ki ho gi aur jo naik amal kere ga, khuwa woh mard ho ya aurat, bashart e kay ho woh momin, aisay sab log jannat mein daakhil hon ge jahan unn ko be hisaab rizaq diya jaye ga"
  40,41,"ae qoum, aakhir yeh kya maajra hai ke mein to tum logon ko nijaat ki taraf bulaataa hon aur tum log mujhe aag ki taraf dawat dete ho !"
  40,42,"tum mujhe is baat ki dawat dete ho ke mein Allah se kufar karoon aur is ke sath unn hstyon ko shareektehraؤں jinhein mein nahi jaanta, halaank mein tumhe uss zabardast mughfirat karne walay khuda ki taraf bulaa raha hon"
  40,43,"nahi, haq yeh hai aur iss ke khilaaf nahi ho sakta ke jin ki taraf tum mujhe bulaa rahay ho unn ke liye nah duniya mein koi dawat hai nah akhirat mein, aur hum sab ko palatna Allah hi ki taraf hai, aur hadd se guzarnay walay aag mein jaane walay hain"
  40,44,"aaj jo kuch mein keh raha hon, anqareeb woh waqt aeye ga jab tum ussay yaad karo ge aur apna maamla mein Allah ke supurd karta hon, woh apne bundon ka nigehbaan hai """
  40,45,"aakhir kaar unn logon ne jo buri se buri chaalein uss momin ke khilaaf chalein, Allah ne unn sab se uss ko bacha liya, aur firaon ke saathi khud bad tareen azaab ke phair mein aa gay"
  40,46,"dozakh ki aag hai jis ke samnay subah o shaam woh paish kiye jatay hain, aur jab qayamat ki gharri aa jaye gi to hukum ho ga ke all firaon ko shadeed tar azaab mein daakhil karo"
  40,47,"phir zara khayaal karo uss waqt ka jab yeh log dozakh mein aik dosray se jhagar rahay hon ge duniya mein jo log kamzor thay woh barray ban'nay walon se kahin ge ke"" hum tumahray tabay thay, ab kya yahan tum naar jahannum ki takleef ke kuch hissay se hum ko bacha lau ge? """
  40,48,"woh barray ban'nay walay jawab den ge"" hum sab yahan aik haal mein hain, aur Allah bundon ke darmain faisla kar chuka hai """
  40,49,"phir yeh dozakh mein parre hue log jahannum ke ahal karon se kahin ge"" apne rab se dua karo ke hamaray azaab mein bas aik din ki takhfeef kar day """
  40,50,"woh poucheen ge"" kya tumahray paas tumahray rasool bayyaynaat le kar nahi atay rahay thay ?"" woh kahin ge"" haan"" jahannum ke ahal car bolein ge :"" phir to tum hi dua karo, aur kafiroon ki dua akart hi jaane wali hai """
  40,51,"yaqeen jano ke hum apne Rasolo-n aur imaan laane walon ki madad iss duniya ki zindagi mein bhi laziman karte hain, aur uss roz bhi karen ge jab gawah kharray hon ge ,"
  40,52,jab zaalmon ko un ki moazrat kuch bhi faida nah day gi aur unn par laanat parre gi aur bad tareen thikana unn ke hissay mein aeye ga
  40,53,aakhir dekh lau ke moose ki hum ne rahnumai ki aur bani Israel ko is kitaab ka waris bana diya
  40,54,jo aqal o Danish rakhnay walon ke liye hadaayat o nasiyaat thi
  40,55,"pas ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, sabr karo, Allah ka wada Bar haq hai, apne qasoor ki maffi chaho aur subah o shaam apne rab ki hamd ke sath is ki tasbeeh karte raho"
  40,56,"haqeeqat yeh hai ke jo log kisi sanad o Hujjat ke baghair jo unn ke paas aayi ho, Allah ki ayaat mein jhagrre kar rahay hain unn ke dilon mein kibar bhara howa hai, magar woh uss barayi ko pounchanay walay nahi hain jis ka woh ghamand rakhtay hain bas Allah ki panah maang lau, woh sab kuch daikhta aur santa hai"
  40,57,"asmano aur zameen ka peda karna insanon ko peda karne ki bah nisbat yaqeenan ziyada bara kaam hai, magar aksar log jantay nahi hain"
  40,58,aur yeh nahi ho sakta ke andha aur Beena yaksaa ho jaye aur imandaar o Saleh aur bad krrdar barabar therain magar tum log kam hi kuch samajte ho
  40,59,"yaqeenan qayamat ki gharri anay wali hai, is ke anay mein koi shak nahi, magar aksar log nahi mantay"
  40,60,"tumhara rab kehta hai"" mujhe poukaro, mein tumhari duayen qubool karoon ga, jo log ghamand mein aa kar meri ibadat se mun morty hain, zaroor woh zaleel o khawar ho kar jahannum mein daakhil hon ge """
  40,61,"woh Allah hi to hai jis ne tumahray liye raat banai taakay is mein sukoon haasil karo, aur din ko roshan kya haqeeqat yeh hai ke Allah logon par bara fazl frmane wala hai magar aksar log shukar ada nahi karte"
  40,62,wohi Allah ( jis ne tumahray liye yeh kuch kya hai ) tumhara rab hai har cheez ka khaaliq is ke siwa koi mabood nahi phir tum kidhar se b_hkaye ja rahay ho ?
  40,63,isi terhan woh sab log b_hkaye jatay rahay hain jo Allah ki ayaat ka inkaar karte thay
  40,64,woh Allah hi to hai jis ne tumahray liye zameen ko jaye qarar banaya aur oopar aasman ka gunbad bana diya jis ne tumhari soorat banai aur barri hi umdah banai jis ne tumhe pakeeza cheezon ka rizaq diya wohi Allah ( jis ke yeh kaam hain ) tumhara rab hai be hisaab barkatoon wala hai woh kaayenaat ka rab
  40,65,wohi zindah hai uss ke siwa koi mabood nahi usi ko tum poukaro apne deen ko is ke liye khalis kar ke saari tareef Allah Rab alaalmin hi ke liye hai
  40,66,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, inn logon se keh do ke mujhe to unn hstyon ki ibadat se mana kar diya gaya hai jinhein tum Allah ko chore kar pkarte ho ( mein yeh kaam kaisay kar sakta hon ) jabkay mere paas mere rab ki taraf se بینات aa chuki hain mujhe hukum diya gaya hai ke mein rab alaalmin ke agay sar-e tasleem khham kar dun"
  40,67,"wohi to hai jis ne tum ko matti se peda kya, phir nutfay se, phir khoon ke lothrayse, phir woh tumhe bachay ki shakal mein nkalta hai, phir tumhe berhata hai taakay tum apni poori taaqat ko poanch jao, phir aur berhata hai taakay tum burhapay ko pohncho aur tum mein se koi pehlay hi wapas bulaa liya jata hai yeh sab kuch is liye kya jata hai taakay tum apne muqarrar waqt taq poanch jao, aur is liye ke tum haqeeqat ko samjhoo"
  40,68,"wohi hai zindagi dainay wala, aur wohi mout dainay wala hai woh jis baat ka bhi faisla karta hai, bas aik hukum deta hai ke woh ho jaye aur woh ho jati hai"
  40,69,"tum ne dekha unn logon ko jo Allah ki ayaat mein jhagrre karte hain, kahan se woh phira-ay ja rahay hain ?"
  40,70,yeh log jo iss kitaab ko aur unn saari kitabon ko jutlatay hain jo hum ne apne Rasolo-n ke sath bhaije theen? anqareeb inhen maloom ho jaye ga
  40,71,"jab taoq un ki gardnon mein hon ge, aur zanjeeren, jin se pakar kar"
  40,72,woh kholtey hue pani ki taraf kheinchain jayen ge aur phir dozakh ki aag mein jhonk diye jayen ge
  40,73,phir unn se poocha jaye ga ke ab kahan hain Allah ke siwa woh dosray khuda jin ko tum shareek karte thay ?
  40,74,"woh jawab den ge"" khoye gay woh hum se, balkay hum is se pehlay kisi cheez ko nah pkarte thay"" iss terhan Allah kafiroon ka gumraah hona muhaqqiqkar day ga"
  40,75,"unn se kaha jaye ga"" yeh tumhara injaam is liye howa hai ke tum zameen mein ghair haq par magan thay aur phir uss par itratay thay"
  40,76,"ab jao, jahannum ke darwazon mein daakhil ho jao hamesha tum ko wahein rehna hai, bohat hi bura thikana hai mutakbrin ka """
  40,77,"pas ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, sabr karo, Allah ka wada brhq hai ab khuwa hum tumahray samnay hi inn ko unn buray nataij ka koi hissa dikha den jin se hum aِnhin dara rahay hain, ya ( uss se pehlay ) tumhe duniya se utha len, palat kar aana to aِnhin hamari hi taraf hai"
  40,78,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, tum se pehlay hum bohat se rasool bhaij chuke hain jin mein se baaz ke halaat hum ne tum ko betaye hain aur baaz ke nahi betaye kisi rasool ki bhi yeh taaqat nah thi ke Allah ke azan ke baghair khud koi nishani le aata phir jab Allah ka hukum agaya to haq ke mutabiq faisla kar diya gaya aur uss waqt ghalat car log khasaray mein par gay"
  40,79,Allah hi ne tumahray liye yeh maweshi janwar banaye hain taakay un mein se kisi par tum sawaar ho aur kisi ka gosht khao
  40,80,un ke andar tumahray liye aur bhi bohat se munafe hain woh is kaam bhi atay hain ke tumahray dilon mein jahan jaane ki haajat ho wahan tum unn par poanch sakuu unn par bhi aur kashtiyon par bhi tum sawaar kiye jatay ho
  40,81,"Allah apni yeh nishanain tumhe dikha raha hai, aakhir tum uss ki kin kin nshanyon ka inkaar karo ge"
  40,82,"phir kya yeh zameen mein chalay phiray nahi hain ke inn ko unn logon ka injaam nazar aata jo inn se pehlay guzar chuke hain? woh inn se tadaad mein ziyada thay, inn se barh kar taaqatwar thay, aur zameen mein inn se ziyada shandaar assaar chore gay hain jo kuch kamaai onhon ne ki thi, aakhir woh unn ke kis kaam aayi ?"
  40,83,"jab un ke rasool un ke paas bayyinaat le kar aeye to woh usi ilm mein magan rahay jo un ke apne paas tha, aur phir usi cheez ke phair mein aa gay jis ka woh mazaq uratay thay"
  40,84,jab unhon ne hamara azaab dekh liya to pukaar utthay ke hum ne maan liya Allah wahdah laa shareek ko aur hum inkaar karte hain unn sab mabodon ka jinhein hum shareektehratay thay
  40,85,"magar hamara azaab dekh lainay ke baad un ka imaan unn ke liye kuch bhi nafea nah ho sakta tha, kyunkay yahi Allah ka muqarrar zabita hai jo hamesha is ke bundon mein jari raha hai, aur is waqt kafir log khasaray mein par gay"
